{"tid":94220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟曹星如定崔健邦好打啲？","createTime":"2017-01-25T05:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T16:04:33.000Z","uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce434a6956c5dcb663a7a8d0a36dea2bb6002bf","tid":94220,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"曹星如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n崔健邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曹星如是香港首位職業西洋拳拳擊手，曾任教練，為2012年亞洲洲際金腰帶得主。職業生涯至今保持不敗，錄得 20 連勝，被傳媒冠以「神奇小子」的外號。2017年1月2日，國際拳擊賽主辦單位「世界拳擊組織（WBO）」公佈 2016 年 12 月的拳手排名，曹星如力壓墨西哥拳手 Juan Hernandez，登上超蠅量級拳手第一位，也是第一位能達到該個排名的香港拳手。<br />\n<br />\n藝人崔建邦（Amigo）自18歲開始打西洋拳，而下月17日他將重踏擂台參加由FFG與AEG合辦的《E1 World Championship 2017》，與來自世界各地的業餘拳手較量。Amigo相當重視這場比賽，早於4月已開始進行訓練，近日他更抛下女友李怡隻身飛赴菲律賓，向當地知名拳王Bernabe Concepcion進行為期近一個月的特訓。 <br />\n崔健邦於早前拳賽中敗給15歲的英國對手，不過雖敗不辱，加上母親、圈中好友及無綫高層都齊為他吶喊助威，令他賽後多次感動得眼泛淚光。他表示被對手打裂耳膜，要慢慢復原。<br />\n崔健邦"},{"pid":"37e63bf4d7ee0a50eef5ec5d97d8c7f69df057bb","tid":94220,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"我認為崔健邦好打啲<br />\n起碼敢打女人同黑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddd8c5e160aa9ac89693ba551278da3ab8d1ef8","tid":94220,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60b847fab1a5316d6676623a355988506ca7454","tid":94220,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1137a36f5f42f29d86980c7bd6593c9debb64fdd","tid":94220,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:15:03.000Z","ms